text: Eadward king gret his bisceopas & his abbodas & his heorlas & þeignas þe on þam scyran syndon þe Ordric abbud hæf land inne.
& ic kyþe eow þæt ic hæbbe geunnon him into Sancta Mariam mynstre sace & socne, toll & team & infangeneþeof binnan burgon & butan burgon, hamsocne & griðbrice & foresteal ofer his agen land.
And ic nelle <nanum> men geþafian þæt him ænig þara þinga of anime þe ic him geunnen hebbe.
